CustomField.description: Time between case open to first reported PSE outcome
CustomField.formula: (ROUND( MOD( ( FirstTimeReportedPSEOutcome__c - CreatedDate ) * 24 * 60, 60 ), 0 )+ FLOOR( MOD( (FirstTimeReportedPSEOutcome__c - CreatedDate ) * 24, 24 ) )*60+ FLOOR( FirstTimeReportedPSEOutcome__c - CreatedDate )*60*24)/60
CustomField.label: Time To Report First PSE Outcome (Hr)
